description:
## Content

List of members of Chamber of Deputies of Romania in 2016-2020 and 2020-2024.

## Collection

Scrapped from 2 Wikipedia pages:
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_members_of_the_Chamber_of_Deputies_of_Romania_(2016%E2%80%932020)  
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_members_of_the_Chamber_of_Deputies_of_Romania_(2020%E2%80%932024)

## Inspiration

Analyze the distribution of chairs per political party in the 2 legislatures (2016-2020 and 2020-2024). Observe if some individuals migrated from one party to another. See which members of the Parliament maintained their constituencies or changes it from one legislature to the next.
title: Members of Romanian Chamber of Deputies
